"""# File Handling

* Basic Operations: Open, Read, Write, and Close.
* Syntax: open(filename, mode)
* File Modes: \\
`'r'`: Read (default). \\
`'w'`: Write (overwrites existing content). \\
`'a'`: Append (adds to the existing content). \\
`'rb'`, `'wb'`, `'ab'`: Modes for binary files. \\
`'r+'`, `'w+'`, `'a+'`: Read and write combined. \\
"""

